snippet.title: Pineview Drive - Rising Storm - A direct comparsion of the old and new visuals
snippet.description: This video shows the difference between the first version of the intro of Pineview Drive - Rising Storm and the new version with the new engine version. The new version is still unfinished, but it cleary shows the reason why we decided to invest more time in this project to bringt the whole game to a higher visual level.
